Package: sophistication
Type: Package
Title: Functions to help measure textual sophistication
Version: 0.70
Author: Kenneth Benoit [aut, cre], Arthur Spirling [aut], and Kevin Munger [aut]
Maintainer: Kenneth Benoit <kbenoit@lse.ac.uk>
Description: Provides functionality to calibrate and estimate measures of
    textual sophistication and reading difficulty. Used in Benoit, Kenneth, 
    Kevin Munger, and Arthur Spirling. (2019) "Measuring and Explaining 
    Political Sophistication Through Textual Complexity."
    American Journal of Political Science 63(2, April): 491â€“508. 
    10.1111/ajps.12423
